PrecisGENERAL AMENDING REGULATIONS (TRAVELLERS' REPORTING EXEMPTION) amending the following regulations to allow residents, returning to Canada by private vehicle at a highway border crossing, to make only an oral report of their goods to claim their traveller's exemption, effective September 1, 1995: . - Reporting of Imported Goods Regulations - Accounting for Imported Goods and Payment of Duties Regulations .
